channel.title: I have a problem
channel.description:
ok this is my problem and i find this reall f**ked up any ways i looked into this and it seems that my server isn't even reading my client.java i even did some test's to see what is wrong with it and i deleted client.java from my server folder and i went to compile normally i would get a shit load of errors and my server wouldn't work but some how i got no errors and i ran the server and the funny thing is my server was up and i logged into it without putting my server ip in or having my client.java in my server folder i know this all sounds weird for u all but it's the honest to god truth i swear on my dead mothers grave this is happening and it all started to happen when i was testing the teleblock spell to try and get it working again but for the test all i did was i took a "stock untouched" client.java i had from the past from the same source as my server and tryed tb to see if it worked and it did then i went to try and fix the tb on my server's client.java to see what was wrong so i put my client.java back in "the one i worked on the most" and i edited the teleblock spell and i know it would work after i was done editing and i went to compile and these are the errors i get.....now remember my server f**king runs without my client.java in it and it'm getting creeped out and i by all my server members are mad cause they can't get on it "i don't wanna put my server up with this bug" so heres my errors i get when i compile......
[code] client.java:23982: illegal start of type if ((EnemyHP - hitDiff) < 0) { ^ client.java:23986: <identifier> expected mageXP = (hitDiff * 500); ^ client.java:23987: invalid method declaration; return type required addSkillXP(mageXP, 6); ^ client.java:23987: <identifier> expected addSkillXP(mageXP, 6); ^ client.java:23987: ')' expected addSkillXP(mageXP, 6); ^ client.java:23988: invalid method declaration; return type required addSkillXP(hitDiff, 3); ^ client.java:23988: <identifier> expected addSkillXP(hitDiff, 3); ^ client.java:23988: ')' expected addSkillXP(hitDiff, 3); ^ client.java:23990: <identifier> expected castOnPlayer.hitDiff = hitDiff; ^ client.java:23991: <identifier> expected castOnPlayer.KillerId = playerId; ^ client.java:23992: <identifier> expected castOnPlayer.updateRequired = true; ^ client.java:23993: <identifier> expected castOnPlayer.hitUpdateRequired = true; ^ client.java:23996: 'class' or 'interface' expected public boolean AttackNPC() { ^ client.java:25677: 'class' or 'interface' expected public boolean healing() { ^ client.java:28864: 'class' or 'interface' expected public PlayerSave loadMythgame(String playerName, String playerP ass) ^ client.java:30749: 'class' or 'interface' expected } ^ client.java:30749: 'class' or 'interface' expected } ^ 17 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
can't some one help me out?
